cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method to improve the robustness of deep neural networks for image classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed method involves augmenting the classification pipeline with shock absorbing robust features, which can be seen as a form of data augmentation or regularization, falling under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
